Mbali fana vayandikile mbuli zilongigwe, "Chilongele, muhavu mulume sekeyamsole muke."
Mbali kwaviya mulume komtendela uzinzi muke wake yaidumwe na mulume komtendela uzinzi muke wake, na mulume komtendela uzinzi muke wake."
