Mbali nowalongela ivo kwa ichimu cha kumulekelela, mbali si kwa kumulamba.
"Nolonda wanhu wose wakale fana niye na wayage. Mbali munhu yoyose yonda yaweng'he hela ya Mulungu, niiyo fana ino, hebu ivo ivo."
Ivo nowalongela wanhu wagonekigwe na waja wagane, muhavu wawalekelele fana niye.
Viyaviya waja hawavimanyile bule, wodaha kusoligwa, kufosa kusoligwa na kusoligwa.
Mbali kwa wanhu wagonekigwe, si niye mbali Mndewa yowalongela, muke sekeyamsole mulume.
Viyaviya yahaleka muke iyo, mulume kolondeka mulumake, na mulume sekeyamsole muke wake."
Wanhu wamwenga nowalongela, niye, si Mndewa, vino. Munhu yoyose yeli na muke yeli na uhuwilo, na kolondeka kukala na muke iyo, sekeyamsole.
Viyaviya muke yeli na mulume yoyakalile na uhuwilo, na muke yoyalawe na muke iyo, sekeyamsole mulume iyo.
Kwaviya mulume yoyose yonda yatogole kezakomboligwa, na muke yoyose yoyatogole kezakomboligwa na ndugu yake. Hata ivo wana wenu wakala wabule uhasanyi, mbali wawo ni yelile."
Na munhu yoyose yeli na uhuwilo wahaigola, sekewamsola. Ndugu yake hebu lumbu jake hadaha kumsola mgane ino, ila Mulungu kawatanga kwa tindiwalo.
Viyaviya vinoga, muke, vino vinoga kumuhonya mulume? Viyaviya vinoga, mulume, vinoga kumuhonya muke wake?
One Mndewa sigambe chila chinhu chochose chiya chayadahile, chila munhu yoyawasagule Mulungu, niivo mwing'heni. Na ivo niivo nowalagiliza mwii zikaye zose."
Mng'hali hanhu hana didugila, niye sizagumigwa? Hanhu hanhu hanogile hanhu hana didugila da Pasaka, niye sizagumigwa."
