Viyavimanyile muke wake? sekeyamulondile mfungwa. Viyaviya komulonda muke wake? sekeyamulonda muke wake.
Viyaviya one usola, hautenda uhasanyi. Na one umsola mgane, hautenda uhasanyi. Mbali lukuli lwa wanhu weli na udahi wa kutenda yayo, mbali niye nizawahonya."
"Chilongele mbuli ino, wandugu zangu, zisiku zifika. Viyaviya wanhu weli na wanaake welibule wanaake, sekewalongele.
Na waja wowakalile woja, sekewalekelele kulila. Na waja wowakalile wogaya, sekewalekelele kulila. Na waja wowakalile woja, sekewalekelele chinhu.
Na waja wolonda vinhu va isi sekewavwizile bule. Kalonga vino kwaviya ni vinhu va isi ino.
"Chilongele mbuli inogile. Munhu yoyosola ni ya Mndewa, yoyamtendele Mndewa, fana viyotogola Mndewa.
Mbali munhu yoyosola walava usungu wa isi ino, vino kamulonda muke wake?
Viyaviya muke yelibule mulume, na mndele yoyosola komdalisa Mndewa, kolondeka yawe munhu yelile muhala, mbali lukuli lwake na muhe wake. Mbali mwanamke yelibule muke fana viyalonda isi ino, vino vinoga bule kumulonda mulume?
Ivo nowalongela mbuli ino kwa ludabwa, siwalongela bule kwa ichimu cha kumulekelela, ila kwa ichimu cha kumuwonela ubazi na kumwing'ha Mndewa bila kudanganika."
Viyaviya munhu yoyose yondayamuwone mgane wake kavimanya kuwa kasola, sekeyawalekelele mgane iyo, yalekigwe fana viyalondile. Hachitenda uhasanyi, kolondeka kusoligwa.
Kwaviya munhu yeli na udahi mkulu muumoyo wake kwaviya habule chinhu chochimtenda yambule mwiko, mbali kana udahi wa kulola chinhu chochose, na kana udahi mkulu muumoyo wake, yadahe kuigola mwenyewo, katenda vinogile.
